    "autumn_sale_media_comments_6dhjFb": {
      "type": "autumn-sale-media-comments",
      "blocks": {
        "media_wbbaeK": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/2_acb06d4f-6c1f-4583-a76d-8c2d9c48c354.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/2_acb06d4f-6c1f-4583-a76d-8c2d9c48c354.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>Great product. Excellent communication and fast shipping. Bike was exactly as described and did not disappoint from the unpacking to my last ride! Jasionbike is our brand Only fault was mine, should have ordered one for my wife!!</p>",
            "title": "Michael R."
          }
        },
        "media_6Fq4TE": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/7_162f3256-a6b0-41a7-bb56-55c01b642e94.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/7_162f3256-a6b0-41a7-bb56-55c01b642e94.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>These bikes are the bomb!!!!!! Completely satisfied with our purchase of two Hunter Pro bikes. Easy to assemble, a very short learning curve - and an intuitive app.</p>",
            "title": "Hazer"
          }
        },
        "media_EQqnDg": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/5_cca13ef3-16b4-4122-bcc8-34f8328b75e2.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/5_cca13ef3-16b4-4122-bcc8-34f8328b75e2.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>The retro revolt pro bike is the greatest bike I’ve ever ridden I like it so much I’m thinking about becoming a dealer or buying a couple dozen and reselling them!</p>",
            "title": "Raspy Rides"
          }
        },
        "media_aDaPiY": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/1_fbd9bec1-285d-418d-bf15-f117161676c3.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/product-image2.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>My husband has enjoyed this e-bike! It’s great for the price point. He likes that it has gears. The seat is very comfortable. The bike came within 2 weeks.</p>",
            "title": "Annette S. "
          }
        },
        "media_aX9Kyq": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/3_5c036d94-8611-471f-980c-652507a75acb.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/3_5c036d94-8611-471f-980c-652507a75acb.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>This was a gift bought for my husband. He takes it hunting and to pull deer out of the woods. He said it rides very smooth even on rough terrain.</p>",
            "title": "Papa"
          }
        }
      },
